# Link to this sectionTFLite, ONNX, CoreML, TensorRT 내보내기#

📚 이 가이드는 학습된 YOLOv5 🚀 모델을 [PyTorch](https://www.ultralytics.com/glossary/pytorch)에서 ONNX, TensorRT, CoreML 등 다양한 배포 형식으로 내보내는 방법을 설명합니다.

## Link to this section시작하기 전에#

Clone repo and install [requirements.txt](https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5/blob/master/requirements.txt) in a [**Python >=3.8.0**](https://www.python.org/) environment, including [**PyTorch >=1.8**](https://pytorch.org/get-started/locally/). [Models](https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5/tree/master/models) and [datasets](https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5/tree/master/data) download automatically from the latest YOLOv5 [release](https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5/releases).
    
    
    git clone https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5 # clone
    cd yolov5
    pip install -r requirements.txt # install

[TensorRT](https://developer.nvidia.com/tensorrt) 내보내기 예제(GPU 필요)는 Colab [노트북](https://colab.research.google.com/github/ultralytics/yolov5/blob/master/tutorial.ipynb#scrollTo=VTRwsvA9u7ln&line=2&uniqifier=1) 부록 섹션을 참조하십시오. [![Open In Colab](https://colab.research.google.com/assets/colab-badge.svg)](https://colab.research.google.com/github/ultralytics/yolov5/blob/master/tutorial.ipynb)

## Link to this section지원되는 내보내기 형식#

YOLOv5 추론은 공식적으로 12가지 형식을 지원합니다:

성능 팁

  * 최대 3배의 CPU 속도 향상을 위해 ONNX 또는 OpenVINO로 내보내십시오. [CPU 벤치마크](https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5/pull/6613)를 참조하십시오.
  * 최대 5배의 GPU 속도 향상을 위해 TensorRT로 내보내십시오. [GPU 벤치마크](https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5/pull/6963)를 참조하십시오.



형식| `export.py --include`| 모델  
---|---|---  
[PyTorch](https://pytorch.org/)| -| `yolov5s.pt`  
[TorchScript](/ko/integrations/torchscript)| `torchscript`| `yolov5s.torchscript`  
[ONNX](/ko/integrations/onnx)| `onnx`| `yolov5s.onnx`  
[OpenVINO](/ko/integrations/openvino)| `openvino`| `yolov5s_openvino_model/`  
[TensorRT](/ko/integrations/tensorrt)| `engine`| `yolov5s.engine`  
[CoreML](/ko/integrations/coreml)| `coreml`| `yolov5s.mlmodel`  
[TensorFlow SavedModel](/ko/integrations/tf-savedmodel)| `saved_model`| `yolov5s_saved_model/`  
[TensorFlow GraphDef](/ko/integrations/tf-graphdef)| `pb`| `yolov5s.pb`  
[TensorFlow Lite](/ko/integrations/tflite)| `tflite`| `yolov5s.tflite`  
[TensorFlow Edge TPU](/ko/integrations/edge-tpu)| `edgetpu`| `yolov5s_edgetpu.tflite`  
[TensorFlow.js](/ko/integrations/tfjs)| `tfjs`| `yolov5s_web_model/`  
[PaddlePaddle](/ko/integrations/paddlepaddle)| `paddle`| `yolov5s_paddle_model/`  
  
